<section class="mb-6" id="roadmap">
  <h2>8. Roadmap items to plan for</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>GitHub App installation access tokens</strong> for the Agent Tasks API are on GitHub's roadmap. When delivered, partners will be able to issue tasks without depending on an individual user's token, which simplifies background automation. Design the partner's token-handling layer so it can absorb a server-to-server path alongside the current user-to-server one.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Copilot Pro and Pro+ plan support</strong> is also stated as "coming soon." Partners targeting smaller teams should plan their plan-detection logic accordingly.
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>
